S.FORM: Dalia Grybauskait Mntucing hngkawas 1956 idas 3 jiyax 1 ka Dalia Grybauskait ga, empklaw ka hiya. Bukung klwaan Lithuania ta sayang o kiya ka Dalia Grybauskait , pnaah hngkawas 2009 idas 7 jiyax 12 pnrajing kmlawa klwaan. Dalia Grybauskait Kari Lithuania: Dalia Grybauskait , kngkawas 1956 idas 3 diyax 1 ), mntuting Suryeyn cida Lithuania sotu Vilnius, kiya ka Lithuania seyji jnwu, hiya u mnngalan Lithuania Waycyawbu Huku Bucyo mi Caycngbu Bucyo, kiya u mniq kngkawas 2004 prading ngalan Omong Yingkay seykining keykaku mi yosang Caycng na Ying. Kngkawas 2009 idas 5 diyax 17 Soto seyngkyo cida u Dalia Grybauskait ka wada mbiyax mangal Soto. Idas 7 diyax 12, Dalia Grybauskait u wada mdhu bay psdhuwan phiyu Soto, wada mwaya bay rikisi Lithuania tu1 qridin Soto. Ndanan Dalia Grybauskait pa mntuting Lithuania sotu Vilnius, Dalia Grybauskait u kngkawas 1983 mnhdu muyas Leningrader Pyasan Tubeyhing Zhdanov Keyjayswey cwanyey, bukuy daw qmpah mniq Lithuania Ksweyweyn. Kngkawas 1990 babaw dukuricu ka Lithuania daw, Dalia Grybauskait pa ngalan seykining Lithuania Keyjay Sweyweyn Ksweybu. Dalia Grybauskait u kngkawas 1991 cida musa Amirika Pyasan Tubeyhing George muyas pkrana knkla, tbrinah qnlhangan daw ngalan Kwoci Keyjay Hcwobu Ocos seykining niya. Kndusan quri seyji Kngkawas 1990 mlatac Suryeyn dukuricu ka Lithuania daw, kngkawas 1993 wada hdilan Waycyawbu Keyjay Hcwos Scang, kngkawas 1994 cida skulan ngalan Omong Kongs, kngkawas 1996 daw wada ngalan tnpusu Amirika Kongs. Kngkawas 1999, Dalia Grybauskait u splawa tbrinah qnlhangan, mkala qpahun ngalan Keyjaybu Huku Bucyo, so kawas daw wada ngalan Waycyawbu Huku Bucyo, tumal Lithuania mtmay Omong na pprngawan kari. Omong cida Dalia Grybauskait kngkawas 2004 ngalan rmirih Lithuania na Omong cwanweyn, seykining Omong Caycng uuda yosang qpahang. Soto Kngkawas 2009 idas 5, Dalia Grybauskait pa mniq Lithuania knbeyhing seyngkyo mangal 68.18 hyo, wada mndungus mbiyax mangal Soto. Kngkawas 2014 idas 5 mniq tumn2 kcka meytaq Soto seyngkyo mangal 57.87 mnangal hyo ryu mndungus lmutuc mangal Soto dungan. Kndusan niya nanaq Dalia Grybauskait u ini sturung musa sediq mi uka laqi niya. Uxay wana kari tnpusu kari Lithuania, Dalia Grybauskait pa mkla balay skari Ingkoku, kari Russia mi kari Poland, mkla skari France uri. Dalia Grybauskait pa niqan Mqalux Habuk Kongsotaw uri.
